jobs_results.description:
We are seeking an experienced iOS Developer to join our team at Capgemini in Aguascalientes. As a Senior iOS Software Engineer, you will be responsible for designing and developing innovative technology-based solutions for our clients.

This is an exciting opportunity to work with a dynamic team of technical, functional, and industry specialists who are passionate about delivering high-quality solutions. You will have the chance to contribute to client satisfaction by providing timely and responsive value-added services and work products.

In this role, you will have the opportunity to:
• Work closely with the Business and development team to design and develop technology-based solutions;
• Drive individual projects from start to finish;
• Develop strong technical skills in Xcode and Swift programming language;
• Collaborate with colleagues to identify and troubleshoot issues;
• Use Bug tracking systems such as JIRA, confluence to record and track defects.

You will also have access to a collaborative environment that embodies the company's values of Honesty, Boldness, Trust, Freedom, Team Spirit, Modesty, and Fun. Our on-boarding program and career development opportunities will help you build your professional skills foundation and plan for your growth.

The estimated annual salary for this position is around $90,000-$120,000 based on the location and required skills.

If you are a motivated and detail-oriented individual who is passionate about software development, we encourage you to apply for this exciting opportunity.
